te":{"pid":"00ff6da88b882356cf9644952f58561e02dcd8f5","tid":1686612,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:29:37.000Z","msg":"預計: 控方話改控其他 撤而家D控罪<br />\n裁判官批準<br />\n<br />\n利申:尻up冇讀過law"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:11:36.000Z","msg":"咪姐係呢堆告唔入就搵其他黎告<br />\non9輸打贏要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T11:44:30.000Z","msg":"唔清楚<br />\n因為睇開新聞既話係落charge前唔洗答辯既階段popo撤控轉控<br />\n<br />\n呢D已經開庭審緊既唔知有冇得咁玩"},{"pid":"a2247567aee4727ac2d2ea966d84e2e1978ac2bb","tid":1686612,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T11:47:19.000Z","msg":"屆時或須修訂控罪？<br />\n<br />\n可以隨便改？"},{"pid":"f5d4b1bc4ddf496e18f22c1126be02b438dc52f2","tid":1686612,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191106/large/1573015871_d4d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191106%2Flarge%2F1573015871_d4d2.jpg&h=6af2db8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》取得由中國品牌<strong>Acebeam</strong>生產、型號<strong>W30</strong>的強光電筒，經過反複對比，確定為前線防暴警員與速龍小隊佩備的其中一款手持電筒。據說明書所示，生產商稱這款電筒為「<span style=\"color: red;\">（白雷射電筒）White Laser Flashlight</span>」，聲稱<span style=\"color: red;\">最遠射程為2,408米</span>，相當於維園至政府總部的直線距離，超出一般筆型電筒近十倍。電筒及說明書上均標有雷射產品標誌，屬「<span style=\"color: green;\">第2M類激光（雷射）產品</span>」，警告不可以直接射向人或動物眼睛。而按機電工程署安全指引，第2M類雷射「<span style=\"color: green;\">不可直視激光光束</span>」，亦「<span style=\"color: green;\">不可將激光光束瞄準任何人的眼睛</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191106/large/1573015914_c532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191106%2Flarge%2F1573015914_c532.jpg&h=e62eaac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者實際試用該支電筒時，發現它所射出的光線極強，就算只是望向照在地上的反射光線亦感到刺眼，輕易即可照到數百米外而亮度絲毫不減，一公里內的電筒光斑清晰可見，並在黑夜中留下一道白色光柱。惟當射到逾一公里外的建築物時，圓形光斑的邊緣會隨距離增加而開始潰散。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191106/large/1573015917_7822.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191106%2Flarge%2F1573015917_7822.jpg&h=7106f758&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd0c824347c8254a58feda233b927d3dafaef9a3","tid":1686612,"uid":111898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdb1a10eeb2e28c5020ea80430f86946dd5fb5d0","tid":1686612,"uid":121146,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:17:57.000Z","msg":"告唔入  改法例改到入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ON9香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:35:33.000Z","msg":"仲要係官改例 做埋控方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3eee45a23b49a96f9c3316cabce4aaab9496934","tid":1686612,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9134ae33145a2fa105696586626288c067044b0e","tid":1686612,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:24:50.000Z","msg":"雨傘期間大把差佬夾口供係法院比辯方篤爆<br />\n法官唔理照判監"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T03:40:10.000Z","msg":"講左司法已死<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sLhPu3Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsLhPu3Z.jpg&h=715d9001&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n快聚快散！不要跟日程表！be water不要被狗提早佈陣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i3GwJo1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi3GwJo1.jpg&h=1d41d6a0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"}]}